Frequently Asked Questions

Q: Do I need an account to use F1tX?
A: No. You can get started without creating an account. Your progress is stored securely on your device.

Q: How many plans can I generate per week?
A: You can generate up to 3 workout and 3 nutrition plans per week to keep things focused and realistic.

Q: Will I lose my data if I reinstall the app?
A: Data is currently stored locally on your iPhone. If you uninstall the app, your saved data may be removed.

Q: Can I share my progress or awards with friends?
A: Sharing features are planned for future updates. Right now, all your progress stays private to you.

Q: Does F1tX need an internet connection?
A: An internet connection is needed for plan generation and updates. Logging workouts and meals works offline.
